author: @miyabihyatt
text:
This is totally the kind of song that makes me think the combination of Jeno and Yangyang is like a match made in heaven! They sound just too great together!

I absolutely love the song and i loved how Jeno really hyped the crowd, his performance style really suits that song perfectly!

Yuta's style really suit that song too! His rockstar aura gives a lot to the performance!

Jisung's singing in the song is really refreshing, I've always loved his voice so it was great to see him carry most vocal parts with Yuta

Jaemin's rap style gives a stylish style to the song, it's great to see him having strong parts in the song

Yangyang shines the most with Jeno in this song for me! I love his rap style and his energy

I love Hendery's energy too! His parts are great

As for Winwin, I was pleasantly surprised to see he had a lot of parts even if they are short, so he is present through the song! I still don't think it's the style that suit him the best but I think he did an amazing job for this song!


Overall, it's an extra solid unit and I hope they will be able to have another song one day!
